Package: BribeR
Title: Tools for Analyzing the Vladivideos Corruption Transcripts
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Andres", "Soto Plaza", , "andressotoplaza@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides access to and tools for analyzing the 'Vladivideos'
    corpus, a collection of secret recordings in which Vladimiro Montesinos,
    Peru's intelligence chief under President Alberto Fujimori, is documented
    bribing politicians, judges, military officers, media owners, and
    businesspeople during the 1990s. Includes functions for loading and
    filtering transcripts by speaker or topic, computing transcript-level
    metadata, and exploring relationships between speakers and topics through
    an interactive network visualization application.
URL: https://github.com/jessietrudeau/BribeR
BugReports: https://github.com/jessietrudeau/BribeR/issues
